::Feline::

She moved and took Firearm's arm.  She smiled at him. "I'm very 
pleased to meet you. Perhaps both of you could escort me to the 
dining hall? I would very much enjoy your company gentlemen.  It has 
been such a long time since I have felt safe around others. I thank 
you for that. And thank you both for helping me." She smiled at them 
both and purred softly.
